OL,3,CZoo animals take to mud pools and
OL,4,Cwater to beat hot weather
OL,6,FAnimals at Marwell Zoo have been seen
OL,7,Ftaking a creative approach to keeping
OL,8,Fcool as the hot weather continues
OL,9,Facross the South.
OL,11,FThe Hampshire sanctuary's resident
OL,12,Fwhite rhinos, including baby Amali,
OL,13,Fhave been wallowing in pools of mud to
OL,14,Fstave off the record May temperatures.
OL,16,FRolling in mud helps protect rhinos'
OL,17,Fskin from the sun while also keeping
OL,18,Fthem cool.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
