OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779894668
OL,3,CZoo animals take to mud pools and
OL,4,Cwater to beat hot weather
OL,6,FMarwell's colony of penguins,
OL,7,Fmeanwhile, have been spending much of
OL,8,Ftheir time submerged under water in
OL,9,Ftheir enclosures.
OL,11,FIt comes as amber heat alerts for
OL,12,Fparts of the South West and South East
OL,13,Fhave been extended until tomorrow.
OL,15,FThe UK experienced its warmest May day
OL,16,Fever yesterday, with temperatures
OL,17,Fsoaring to 35 Celsius.
